  "uuid": "d9c85616c99f6aa655ca19f7b1d2cae5",
  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "ARCHITECTURAL DESIGNER",
  "description": "<h2><u><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></u></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work closely with Client, Local consultants, PM, Constructors, Suppliers, Quantity surveyor based on the knowledge and experience of Architectural and Structural design.</li>\n  <li>Preparation of presentations throughout the phase of design development by creating 3d rendered images and initial floor plans.</li>\n  <li>To perform detail design: Detail design development (drawings and specifications)</li>\n  <li>Tender document preparation (tender design brief, scope demarcation)</li>\n  <li>To perform construction phase design: Review of construction material / shop drawing</li>\n  <li>Shop drawing preparation (with drafter), coordination and obtain approval from client or local consultant</li>\n  <li>Periodical site inspection (internal check for quality improvement)</li>\n  <li>Verify site installation works are according to design intent.</li>\n  <li>To liaise with PE's, builders, clients and suppliers all throughout the project lifecycle.</li>\n  <li>Handover submission arrangement with drafter team and project team</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<h2><u><strong>Qualifications:</strong></u></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Bachelor’s Degree in Architecture or a related field.</li>\n  <li>At least 5 years of relevant experience in residential / A&amp;A development projects.</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with local regulations and experience in authority submissions.</li>\n  <li>Strong technical knowledge and attention to detail.</li>\n  <li>Proficiency in Revit, AutoCAD, Lumion, SketchUp, Photoshop, and 3Ds Max.</li>\n  <li>Recognise by Singapore Board of Architect</li>\n  <li>Qualified to be TC</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Other information:</strong></p>\n<p>• Central East, Singapore</p>\n<p>• Monday to Friday</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>You may also email your resume to hr@sevensbuild.com</p>",
